{"tid":1640283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"更正 梁天琦放棄就判刑申請上訴 改為直接打甩定罪","createTime":"2019-10-09T01:57:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-17T14:33:51.000Z","uid":39858,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"3044da1c2ab3d6d93c7ccb862c8ff5e415d998dc","tid":1640283,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"（更正）法官先讀出 梁天琦放棄就判刑申請上訴<br />\n改為直接打甩定罪"},{"pid":"8cd10bd63fa31a75284aaa6d0fe24ad9ecc8ad81","tid":1640283,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:58:45.000Z","msg":"天琦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e5d80f8c7a6f65dbe13dac2a19cc8a7bcfdff6","tid":1640283,"uid":287048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:59:16.000Z","msg":"點解唔兩邊一齊上訴？<br />\n就算定罪上訴失敗，都希望可以減刑"},{"pid":"6098820e75ebe421fa3e719688f18f89bb5d09c2","tid":1640283,"uid":300095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔駛審肯定係泛民律師團嘅屎坑橋"},{"pid":"d8277dcc26121981df3c96532ee6260b4d91f6f6","tid":1640283,"uid":2267,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6098820e75ebe421fa3e719688f18f89bb5d09c2","tid":1640283,"uid":300095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔駛審肯定係泛民律師團嘅屎坑橋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:07:11.000Z","msg":"以當年佢身處唔係暴動區域，而入咗佢煽動暴動罪，理論上係會打得甩。但今時今日香港法律已死，望就望個官係正常人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a572e274e6eb2ebfee16382bdd7fe556b3cec28","tid":1640283,"uid":312125,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:08:20.000Z","msg":"（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a><br />\n<br />\n星期二（10月8日）早上，港鐵就宣布提前在晚上八點停駛，點解政府未卜先知出現動亂？其實政府有心製造一個長期嘅亂局，然後用緊急法立更多惡法，其中最近葉國謙就話要準備封網，呢樣嘢可以對香港抗爭造成極嚴重打擊。<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><ins>斷網可毒啞香港人，新疆前車可鑑</ins></span></strong><br />\n斷網真係落實嘅話，<span style=\"color: red;\">最惡劣係好似新疆咁徹底斷網</span>，只有政府部門先可以上網，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹底封網的話，大家不但難以互通抗爭消息，而且香港訊息難以傳到海外，香港人也難以接收海外消息。西方人對香港嘅了解，只能經過政府嘅官方說法，或極少數流出嘅真相。</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">新疆早在2009年封網，同時限制境外人士到新疆旅遊，斷絕新疆對外聯繫，結果近年就出現新疆集中營。呢方面大家一定要警惕！</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong>大家不能掉以輕心</strong><br />\n或者有人認為政府會顧及香港嘅國際環境唔會輕易斷網，但現在中共已經失去理性，當中央黔驢技窮，損害香港利益而徹底封網並非不可。就好似半年前大家都唸唔到香港已經失去遊行以及戴口罩嘅自由。<br />\n<br />\n本文為節錄，全文請到此瀏覽：<br />\n<br />\n（分析+行動）政府有意部署封網，封網後香港變新疆！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1639585\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1639585</a>"},{"pid":"0691634d84da7cc1fd6c13beb3d266e5ba8b97b7","tid":1640283,"uid":290373,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:09:01.000Z","msg":"聽聞又炒車"},{"pid":"33b7c1ef55e150c784bc738a3f554a1050e3a32c","tid":1640283,"uid":259993,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6098820e75ebe421fa3e719688f18f89bb5d09c2","tid":1640283,"uid":300095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T02:01:51.000Z","msg":"唔駛審肯定係泛民律師團嘅屎坑橋"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T08:59:05.000Z","msg":"佢唔想佢單案變先例影響今次運動被控學生"},{"pid":"5e3884b27aeb8af19560a92273bfb27f8f90cba2","tid":1640283,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3044da1c2ab3d6d93c7ccb862c8ff5e415d998dc","tid":1640283,"uid":39858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-09T01:57:25.000Z","msg":"（更正）法官先讀出 梁天琦放棄就判刑申請上訴<br />\n改為直接打甩定罪"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-10T17:01:32.000Z","msg":"點解你會知道屍體位置"},{"pid":"232506f562db30a127dd3ebaef8ab6ecf104bf8c","tid":1640283,"uid":268123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-16T06:36:03.000Z","msg":"【香城施政報告2019】群策群力 轉危為機<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1656908\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1656908</a><br />\n<br />\n辛苦製作，求手足幫推！！！"},{"pid":"c79eac81be04da3471e3239780d5604babb5da10","tid":1640283,"uid":76690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-17T14:33:51.000Z","msg":"結果點"}]}